                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "This poor hotel worker had an excess of work he had to handle. Not only did he need to clean out the trash within the establishment, but he even had to face monsters that had suddenly appeared while he was on his way to attract more customers... Of course, creatures of malicious intent were not as easy to sweep away as trash, and so he could only flee, venting to customers after regarding the day's ill-fortune...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
